    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For the record, MechCommander mech arms ('barrels') sprites are pre-positioned via baked-in offsets, so their WPos is effectively identical to the 'turret'/torso, meaning z-sorting via WPos wouldn't work there.\n\nI have a work-around for that locally, but I suspect it might be too hacky for OpenRA standards to submit it as-is (especially since none of the official mods need sprite barrels to begin with).\n"
